<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=464&amp;p=2828#p2828"><![CDATA[
Are you clicking on the arrow or on the folder name itself? Under any circumstances, when clicking a folder name itself in the left pane with the mouse, it should show normally in the right pane, irrespective of whether Classic Explorer component of Classic Shell is installed or not.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Wed Apr 17, 2013 10:57 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
